"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Ladies and gentlemenâ€¦ A happy new year from our ğŸª to you all!\\n\\nBarnaby believes 2022 to be the year of Ethereum **L2**s (#L222), and as committed long-term builders of **OÎ** itâ€™s no secret which rollup, we believe, will attract a big chunk of that growth.\\n\\nIn anticipation of this announcement, our ğŸ¤¡ğŸ¤¡ğŸ¤¡ had already shipped **Juggler**ğŸ¤¹ during the holidays. Juggler represents CircusDAO first product to go live and is a V2-style, gas-efficient AMM that is ready to serve the needs of **L2 DeFi** users and protocols alike; crucially, our main product will also rely on it for multiple reasons.\\n\\nWith Juggler out and ready to become one of the largest DEXs on Ethereum L2s, letâ€™s now get on with what our main product (following, â€œthe protocolâ€) is about, and how it will be rolled out.\\n\\n*In a nutshellâ€¦ Barnaby saw the need for a decentralized, yield-bearing store of value on Optimistic Ethereum and saw the opportunity as well, given the most native nature of this protocol, to establish it as the DAO cornerstone product, thereby allowing it to govern the DAO itself, and through it, all of its products.*\\n\\nBarnaby himself got to work, and decided to base this work on the appealing OlympusDAO V2 codebase which was nearing completion at the time, the result is a fully customized, improved, more gas-efficient (much cheaper!) and safer contracts system (some [bugs](https://github.com/OlympusDAO/olympus-contracts/issues/139) were found) that is now ready to be unveiled in 3 phases!\\n\\n## #1: Golden Tickets Crowdsale\\n\\nTLDR;\\n\\n***The crowdsale was engineered to strike the best balance between fairness and attractiveness.*** It has two main purposes: \\n\\n* *to allocate the initial ğŸŸï¸ supply as fairly as possible*\\n* *to bootstrap the main protocol treasury with* **Î**\\n\\nFollowing are all the most important details about it:\\n\\n* *The crowdsale could start anyday from the **15th to the 31st** of January, with or without an announcement*\\n* *The crowdsale will span **30 days***\\n* *The initial exchange rate is **1 ğŸŸï¸ : 1 WETH**. This rate will increase linearly to 1:3*\\n* *There is an individual contribution cap of **3 WETH***\\n* *The purchased ğŸŸï¸ will be **claimable forever**, starting **at the end of the crowdsale***\\n* *All proceedings from the crowdsale accrue into the treasury in order to:*\\n  * *bolster the treasury **excess reserves**, allowing for a **longer runaway** period once staking goes live*\\n  * *guarantee that 1 ğŸŸï¸ will always be **backed by at least 1 WETH***\\n* *The crowdsale includes a generous **unlockable airdrop** for gOHM holders (snapshotted at 11.59PM on 31/12/21 GMT+1)*\\n  * *The crowdsale will unlock the airdrop only if, at least, **1221*** **Î** *was raised*\\n  * *An eligible address can claim if, and only if, the treasury holds a safe enough excess reserves amount in that moment (read below for more on this)*\\n  * *Each address is eligible to claim between **0.01 and 0.03 ğŸŸï¸**, randomly determined by their gOHM holdings at the snapshot*\\n  * *If every eligible address were to claim it, then the total airdropped amount would average **\\\\~1000*** **Î***!*\\n  * Eligible addresses will have **360 days** to claim their airdrop\\n\\nThis all-important event will be held imminently, on OÎ, starting on a yet unannounced day in the 2nd half of January and lasting for 30 days thereafter; it will debut the first of the 3-tokens underpinning the protocol: our prized Golden Tickets (ğŸŸï¸, yea thatâ€™s the token symbol, it used to be golden at least on Windowsâ€¦ but worry not for it can be changed later by governance!).\\n\\n*These expensive and special tickets (we paint them in gold) are indeed worth your admission to the ğŸª and thus in turn your access to all of the features that will be rolled out in the next two phases, described further below.*\\n\\n***The crowdsale was engineered to strike the best balance between fairness and attractiveness.*** It has two main purposes: to allocate the initial ğŸŸï¸ supply as fairly as possible and to bootstrap the main protocol treasury with the most sound currency known to mankind: Ether!\\n\\n*Thatâ€™s right, you will need to purchase your ğŸŸï¸ with ETH or WETH at an initial exchange rate of 1:1 at the opening, which will linearly increase to 1:3 by closing time. Oh, there is also an individual contribution cap of 3 WETH; so, the earlier you buy the better off youâ€™ll be!*\\n\\nPurchased ğŸŸï¸ will be minted right away, but will only become claimable during the claiming window (once the crowdsale is over â†’ âˆ). You can buy tickets on behalf of any address, but you will need access to that address to claim them.\\n\\nAny profit generated throughout the crowdsale from the conversion rate will always be entirely deposited into the protocol treasury as excess reserves. This allows to build up the runaway that will be available to the Main Show (ğŸª) , when the staking phase is rolled out. ***It also guarantees that 1 ğŸŸï¸ will always be backed by at least 1 WETH.***\\n\\n### Unlockable Airdrop\\n\\nIf you are were a gOHM holder at *11.59PM on 31/12/21 GMT+1, then rejoice! For* *the crowdsale contains a most generous airdrop for you, however, it will have to be unlocked and earned* (Hey, nothing that the OHM community couldnâ€™t do!)\\n\\nIndeed, should the crowdsale raise at least 1221 Î, then every eligible address will be allowed to claim a randomly determined amount (between 0,01 and 0,03 ğŸŸï¸) based on its gOHM holdings amount at the snapshot.\\n\\n***If every eligible address were to claim it, the average airdropped amount would be close to \\\\~1000* Î*!***\\n\\n*There is another catch (fair, of course), in order for the unlocked airdrop to become claimable, the treasury excess reserves, at claiming time, must also exceed the prefixed amount of 244.2* Î\\n\\nBut, fear notâ€¦\\n\\n***Once the airdrop is unlocked, eligible addresses will have 30 days x 12 = 360 days to claim it!***\\n\\n## #2: The Main Show\\n\\nIn this second phase, the Balloons token (ğŸˆ) and Main Show (ğŸª) contracts will make their debut, furthermore, every other contracts other than governance will also be deployed.\\n\\n***In other words, this will be the long-awaited moment when rebases, staking rewards and bonds all go live!***\\n\\nğŸˆ: the Balloons is the special rebasing token of the protocol\\n\\nğŸª: the Main Show is the staking and wrapping contract that allows attendees to stake their ğŸŸï¸ for rebasing rewards as well as to wrap them in order to partecipate in governance or to move them cross-chains\\n\\n*Details on this phase will be provided in separate announcement posts and at the documentation pages.*\\n\\n## #3: veDAO\\n\\nThe third phase is the most interesting to Barnaby, and ultimately what we would have been all strifing for.\\n\\nHere, the Cotton Candy governance token is unveiled along with the rest of the decentralized governance system contracts. The DAO can finally take life true to its word.\\n\\n***At this stage, all of the DAO products can be governed entirely on-chain, on OÎ.***\\n\\nâ˜ï¸ğŸ­: vote-escrowed governance token for CircusDAO and all of its governable products. Allows for the locking of voting power in time to exercise proposal and execution controls over the DAO smart contracts.\\n\\nThe DAO contracts themselves are based on the universally trusted Governor Bravo template contracts from OpenZeppelin.\\n\\n*Details on this phase will be provided in separate announcement posts and at the documentation pages.*\",\"timestamp\":1641639474,\"title\":\"Admit One: ğŸŸï¸ Crowdsale!\"},\"digest\":\"sBAhgwDb0WhQc2GQOj1TuJNU-i5GWd8Qo47YTPgZ0h4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x776696aFBAc40978Fa9aa58c79c7eD4b6A0d6865\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"s0qERvqUt_bDL2Q1wWjwHoYvD40f4lB6db